Story_Texts.SourceString: The Blessed Plains were once a sanctuary to those who wield the light.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: The Blessed Plains were once a sanctuary to those who wield the light.

Story_Texts.SourceString: A millennia passed in peace. Then came the Great War.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: A millennia passed in peace. Then came the Great War.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Colossal forces clashed all across the plains.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Colossal forces clashed all across the plains.

Story_Texts.SourceString: When the dust settled, the once magnificent structures had turned to rubble.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: When the dust settled, the once magnificent structures had turned to rubble.

Story_Texts.SourceString: But the light wielders have not wasted the last 1,000 years.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: But the light wielders have not wasted the last 1,000 years.

Story_Texts.SourceString: They rebuilt this sanctuary.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: They rebuilt this sanctuary.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Now, Zerath’s corruption threatens to ruin the Blessed Plains once more.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Now, Zerath’s corruption threatens to ruin the Blessed Plains once more.

Story_Texts.SourceString: With healing light at Zerath’s command, it will be difficult to cleanse this land.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: With healing light at Zerath’s command, it will be difficult to cleanse this land.

Story_Texts.SourceString: Thanks for shedding some light on the situation!
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: Thanks for shedding some light on the situation!

Story_Texts.SourceString: You are the worst person I know.
Story_Texts.LocalizedString: You are the worst person I know.
